"{\"uid\": \"thepinknews.com-2024-07-29-simone-biles-sister-lgbtq-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Simone Biles' sister (L) is a lesbian and has been dating professional softball player Janae Jefferson since 2022 (Instagram: @simonebiles/Getty)  Simone Biles' sister (L) is a lesbian and has been dating professional softball player Janae Jefferson since 2022 (Instagram: @simonebiles/Getty)  Gymnast Simone Biles has made a triumphant return to the Olympics, landing an unprecedented move.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}, {\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the vault, Bilesbecame the first woman to land the Yurchenko double-pike at the Olympics- even though the vault caused Biles to drop out of individual events at the Tokyo Olympics four years ago.\", \"from\": 393, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 456, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"score\": 0.9924615128803714, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yurchenko\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yurchenko_(vault)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While on the vault in 2020,Biles suffered from the \\\"twisties\\\", which involves losing control midair and feeling unable to land the move.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bilescompared the experience to being unable to drive while at the wheel in a car: \\\"Your mind and your body are at a disconnect.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Your body is going to try to do something, and your mind is going to be like, 'No, you are not doing this', I am my car.\\\"\", \"from\": 860, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt like I was fighting my body and my mind to do these tricks,\\\" she told the Call Her Daddy podcast.\", \"from\": 983, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But, it seems that Biles has gotten over the \\\"twisties\\\" and is better than ever at this year's events.\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1192, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is now a favourite for gold in the majority of events in which she will be competing in, while celebrities like Ariana Grande, Lady Gaga, Tom Cruise, and Snoop Dogg -who is a special correspondent for NBC- watched her compete.\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1310, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ariana Grande\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ariana_Grande\"}, {\"begin\": 1325, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1336, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But did you also know that Biles is a major league LGBTQ+ ally as well as a talented sportswoman?\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here are all of the facts.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Adria Biles\\ud83d\\udc51\\ud83c\\udf52\\ud83c\\udf08 (@adria_biles)  Simone Biles is a staunch LGBTQ+ ally, having stood up for the community in many ways in the past.\", \"from\": 1552, \"to\": 1698, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Simone Biles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simone_Biles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her sister, Adria, identifies as a lesbian and has been dating professional softball player Janae Jefferson since 2022.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1715, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\", \"score\": 0.8559506857548911, \"rank\": 0.16829160441480379, \"text\": \"Adria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\"}, {\"begin\": 1795, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janae\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\"}, {\"begin\": 1801, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.550200046661323e-16, \"text\": \"Jefferson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The siblings are incredibly close.\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles has always been incredibly supportive of her sister and accepted her sexuality immediately.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Adria was also a bridesmaid at Simone's wedding, and Adria's girlfriend Janae Jefferson was her plus one.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\", \"score\": 0.8559506857548911, \"rank\": 0.16829160441480379, \"text\": \"Adria\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adriatic_Sea\"}, {\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janae\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janae_Timmins\"}, {\"begin\": 2035, \"end\": 2044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.550200046661323e-16, \"text\": \"Jefferson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_Jefferson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gold medallist has also spoken out about Uganda's regressive anti-homosexuality law, sharing a tweet that read: \\\"For life\\u2026 that's a lil absurd.\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2109, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.306254448402375e-13, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"love is love.\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You all be fighting for the wrong things!\\\"\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Uganda's president Yoweri Museveni signed the country's \\\"gay law\\\", aka the draconian Anti-Homosexuality Act, into effect in 2023, withLGBTQ+ people living in fear of arrest and the death penalty.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2462, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2270, \"end\": 2276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.306254448402375e-13, \"text\": \"Uganda\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uganda\"}, {\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoweri_Museveni\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yoweri Museveni\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoweri_Museveni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yoweri_Museveni\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And in 2020, Biles participated in an ad for Uber Eats alongsideQueer Eye's Jonathan Van Ness.\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2543, \"end\": 2560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Van_Ness\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonathan Van Ness\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Van_Ness\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonathan_Van_Ness\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thisled to an anti-LGBTQ hate group posting a petitionand statement complaining that the ads push the \\\"LGBTQ+ agenda\\\" and using vile language about Van Ness and Biles \\\"glamorising a LGBTQ+ lifestyle\\\"  Biles defended the ad and Van Nessby tweeting: \\\"The world we live in makes me sad, but I'd do x100000 more commercials with you just to piss everyone off.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2915, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The LGBTQIA will always have my support and feel welcome on my socials.\\\"\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2923, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LGBTQIA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LGBT\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Uber Eats also slapped down homophobeswho were angry about the ads.\", \"from\": 2990, \"to\": 3057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokesperson toldNBC News: \\\"At Uber Eats, we are unapologetically committed to representing the flavour spectrum.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From tacos to talent, we like it spicy.\", \"from\": 3176, \"to\": 3216, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"JVN and Simone serve gymnastic prowess and self-confidence, qualities millions of moms everywhere can - and do - support.\\\"\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles is clearly a lifelong LGBTQ+ ally and uses her fame to spread her support for the LGBTQ+ community - in addition to being a gymnastics powerhouse.\", \"from\": 3341, \"to\": 3493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We love to see it.\", \"from\": 3494, \"to\": 3512, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can read all of our Paris Olympics 2024 coveragehere.\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3541, \"end\": 3555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp